description.narrative:
The project aims to ensure that there is a robust technical management system in place for the execution of the Project. It is the expectation that the consultancy will ensure:

-        the articulation of Guyana’s Energy Pathway, inclusive of Renewable Energy;

-        the development of energy sector business models;

-        the establishment of the enabling legal and regulatory frameworks; and

-        the deployment of Energy Efficiency and Renewable Energy Technologies in prioritised sectors.
